Richard Daniels https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Richard_Daniels 0 Richard Daniels (23 January 1864 – 27 January 1939), was a Welsh-born American film actor. He appeared in 27 films between 1922 and 1926. He was born in Gwubach, Wales and died in Los Angeles, California four days after his 75th birthday. He was the father of the Our Gang actor Mickey Daniels. Richard_Daniels ( 23_January_1864 – 27_January_1939 ) , was a_Welsh-born_American_film_actor . He appeared in 27_films between 1922_and_1926 .
